# Optional: only if you are NOT using ./~/.tauri/myapp.key
# Copy to signing.env.local (gitignored) — never commit secrets.

# Preferred on Windows: path to the minisign file from `tauri signer generate -w ...`
# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PATH=

# If you set TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY, paste the **entire myapp.key file** as
# multiline text, OR use the _PATH form above. Do not paste a random base64
# one-liner unless it decodes to minisign text starting with "untrusted comment:".

# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY_PASSWORD=
